## Complete Flow

```text
GitHub
   │
   ▼
Jenkins
   │
   ▼
Checkout Code
   │
   ▼
Build Docker Image
   │
   ▼
Login to ECR
   │
   ▼
Tag Image
   │
   ▼
Push Image to Amazon ECR
   │
   ▼
Amazon ECR Repository
```

This is the standard workflow used in many production CI/CD pipelines. Later, you can extend it to deploy the pushed image automatically to services such as **Amazon Elastic Container Service (ECS)**, **Amazon Elastic Kubernetes Service (EKS)**, or an EC2 instance.
